/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403cb1676da7bd25489a7cfaaf518236ba0cc22a","tid":1574091,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:37:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8255a5867d5374837211a8d19574f9c8a5ccaeae","tid":1574091,"uid":303805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:44:14.000Z","msg":"文宣呀唔好圍爐住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f582ca0c6e359c44ea53cbd497bce027e1162de9","tid":1574091,"uid":301479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6cfc66f7899aabaeb7ff944587098bbae84be5b8","tid":1574091,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T09:22:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GFah9nA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGFah9nA.png&h=adafc92c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n連日來親中撐警人士在多區出動，並與反送中市民發生衝突，昨晚在北角一帶更有懷疑「福建幫」與市民毆鬥。昨晚大陸官媒《環球時報》發表社評，形容在中央支持下，港府及警隊「依靠愛國愛港群眾」控制局面的能力，得到充分顯現。<br />\n<br />\n《環時》在昨晚近11時發表社評，以〈香港社會需營造更強大的共同利益〉為題，指香港參加激進示威的人明顯減少了，但少數暴力示威者仍很猖獗，形容香港處於是繼續惡化與恢復秩序的十字路口。<br />\n<br />\n社評指在中央支持下，「香港特區政府和警隊依靠愛國愛港群眾控制局面的能力得到更充分的顯現，香港局勢有在內部逐漸築底的態勢」。不過要恢復香港秩序，重建法治權威，以至將大部分市民重新凝聚起來，仍有大量工作需要開展。<br />\n<br />\n文章提及香港是自由港並實行資本主義制度，「等於是向西方社會洞開」，美國等要搞滲透最容易，「美國或英國的特工潛入香港，甚至從事活動，如果暴露了，可能不是大事，但如果內地警察與香港警方有什麼合作，反而會被拿來大做文章」。<br />\n<br />\n《環時》認為儘管香港有少數人寧願「攬炒」，但絕大多數港人決不會陪他們這樣玩。社評強調香港要以《基本法》為基礎儘早安定下來，「那些力量把香港政治當成一個國家的事情來要求了，因此碰壁是必然的」。<br />\n<br />\n今次已非大陸官媒首次肯定愛國愛港人士行為。8月3日官媒《人民日報》刊出評論文章，稱堅決支持愛國愛港人士捍衛香港法治的行動，希望港人共同聲討激進分子的犯罪。上月全國政協副主席、前特首梁振英亦撰文，認同必要時可使用「體制外的力量」應對「黑衣暴力運動」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E7%A4%BE%E8%A9%95-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E4%BE%9D%E9%9D%A0%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E6%84%9B%E6%B8%AF%E7%BE%A4%E7%9C%BE%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%B1%80%E9%9D%A2/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25BE%259D%25E9%259D%25A0%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%259D%25A2%2F&d=9iHhAbkmMxvvE1I2I23sbbY5fiapVNQoBN5VkmpLYQk%3D&h=be7aabe0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%2592%25B0%25E6%2599%2582-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258C%2581%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E9%259A%258A%25E4%25BE%259D%25E9%259D%25A0%25E6%2584%259B%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2584%259B%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%25BE%25A4%25E7%259C%25BE%25E6%258E%25A7%25E5%2588%25B6%25E5%25B1%2580%25E9%259D%25A2%2F&h=ce02f543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%92%B0%E6%99%82-%E7%A4%BE%E8%A9%95-%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E6%94%AF%E6%8C%81%E8%AD%A6%E9%9A%8A%E4%BE%9D%E9%9D%A0%E6%84%9B%E5%9C%8B%E6%84%9B%E6%B8%AF%E7%BE%A4%E7%9C%BE%E6%8E%A7%E5%88%B6%E5%B1%80%E9%9D%A2/</a><br />\n<br />\n我地可以名正言順話福建幫黑社會係共產黨操控攻擊市民，警黑合作係共產黨指使<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:02:00.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">Police press conference at 16:00 denies this, so the Hong Kong Police has dis-obey the order from the central government.</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"f9ce089b68dcd9cda155b9122067ea4af0f72144","tid":1574091,"uid":107297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:09:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc1bdaf7ff9601b48675ef52f170d48d32694a0","tid":1574091,"uid":76745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"37e5c307745234c42ab50a122895062ea3a5785a","tid":1574091,"uid":2